{"tid":1723291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"革大討論","createTime":"2019-11-15T06:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T07:12:02.000Z","uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20650cbc39ec4d809be1a85ed3579462e7b7fb90","tid":1723291,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:56:20.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉，小弟想討論吓<span style=\"color: red;\">開返一條行車線嘅可能性</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>討論：</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- PO而家係特登唔做野，玩內耗，死守成本高成效低<br />\n- 已經成功停課（國際生走咗，復課機會低），死守校園意義在於____？係咪可以將資源放去其他地方？<br />\n- 有需要時再返出嚟（如PO入嚟拉人時），到時可能可以號召到更多人入嚟幫手<br />\n- 但係，開返行車線的話，就唔能夠真正完全地癱瘓交通-&gt;癱瘓社會-&gt;攬炒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以上係我暫時諗到的<br />\n唔知大家想法如何"},{"pid":"d5040d610bed94343836e1effd74c5c91a5f5c5d","tid":1723291,"uid":258302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:57:15.000Z","msg":"推唔郁"},{"pid":"4eca4d6c842eecc0dc119a9d75a7631fb5792609","tid":1723291,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:12:02.000Z","msg":"help push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}